paragraphs.title: Average price & Last price
paragraphs.text:
val grouped = ds.
  groupBy(window($"timestamp", "10 minutes").as("window")).
  agg(
    count($"tid").as("count"), 
    avg("price").as("avgPrice"),
    stddev("price").as("stddevPrice"),
    last("price").as("lastPrice"),
    sum("amount").as("sumAmount")
  ).
  select("window.start", "count", "avgPrice", "lastPrice", "stddevPrice", "sumAmount").
  sort("start")

z.show(grouped)

val movingAverage = ds.
  groupBy(window($"timestamp", "1 hour", "2 minutes").as("window")).
  agg(
    avg("price").as("avg1hPrice")
  ).
  select("window.start", "avg1hPrice").
  sort("start")

z.show(movingAverage)
